title: WATCH: Joey Fatone Singing Backstreet Boys...
content:
Back in the '90s and after Y2K, you were either Team Backstreet Boys 's Anthony and Carla Marie were singing Backstreet Boys' "I Want It That Way" while visiting Taiwan recently, when Joey Fatone joined them on stage to sing his rival boyband's chart-topper. And it was glorious. 

He went from *NSYNC-er to Backstreet Boy seamlessly.
